Installing OverCoat

1. Installing Overcoat Tool Properties and Values
	Setup environment variable:
		MAYA_SCRIPT_PATH to this directory (the overcoat_overcoat directory)

 	Alternatively you can copy following files to <MayaInstallDirectory>\scripts\other
		overcoatHairToolProperties
		overcoatHairToolValues 

2. Installing brush images
	Copy the overcoat_Images folder to <MayaInstallDirectory>\icons